[USAGE]:
    signatures_* [File] [Offset of the DATA being encrypted(Byte)] [Length of DATA being encrypted(KB)]
For example:
    X-Boot for NAND Flash:
    ./signatures_spl x-boot-nand.bin 0 6
    Firmware for USB-Tool:
    ./signatures_spl fw_ddr3.bin 0 6
    Firmware for BURNER:
    ./signatures_spl 2G-warrior-unmd5-burner.fw 0 6
    Kernel:
    ./signatures_kernel boot.img 2048 6
    Bootloader:
    ./signatures_bootloader x-boot3.bin 0 6